---
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-(--color-accent)/5 via-transparent to-(--color-accent)/3 dark:from-(--color-dark-accent)/10 dark:to-(--color-dark-accent)/5"></div>
  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-(--color-accent) dark:text-(--color-dark-accent) mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase">Tech Blog</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
      안녕하세요,
      <br />
      <span class="text-(--color-accent) dark:text-(--color-dark-accent)">AI Engineer</span> 오승범입니다.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-(--color-text-secondary) dark:text-(--color-dark-text-secondary) max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
      AI, Python, DevOps 등 기술과 경험을 기록하고 공유하는 공간입니다.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="/blog"
        class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-(--color-accent) dark:bg-indigo-500 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
      >
        블로그 보기
      </a>
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border border-(--color-border) dark:border-(--color-dark-border) text-sm font-medium hover:border-(--color-accent) dark:hover:border-(--color-dark-accent) transition-colors"
      >
        About
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/Sbeom12"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border border-(--color-border) dark:border-(--color-dark-border) text-sm font-medium hover:border-(--color-accent) dark:hover:border-(--color-dark-accent) transition-colors"
      >
        GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-b border-(--color-border) dark:border-(--color-dark-border)"></div>
</section>
